{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1349","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1349/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1349/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1349/events","html_url":"https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1349","id":4531295,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0NTMxMjk1","number":1349,"title":"[2.1.0] Privacy flaw in CI_Upload: file upload w/o extension","user":{"login":"bozma88","id":1729715,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3Mjk3MTU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1729715?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88","html_url":"https://github.com/bozma88","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bozma88/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2012-05-11T10:32:55Z","updated_at":"2012-05-11T10:43:08Z","closed_at":"2012-05-11T10:43:08Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Hi there.\n\nFound an issue in Upload library (Ci 2.1.0).\n\nIf you allow uploads with any extension setting <$config['allowed_types'] = '*';>, this automatically allows uploading of files without extensions.\n\nIn my case this is a wanted feature, but there's a bug in the <get_extension> function: without an extension separator ('.'), the WHOLE ORIGINAL filename is returned as the extension.\n\nThis leads to a security-privacy flaw if you had chosen to encrypt the original filename (it becomes the extension).\n\nHere's a quick suggested but not thoroughly tested solution:\n\n``` php\nclass MY_Upload extends CI_Upload {\n\n    public function get_extension($filename)\n    {\n        if (!strpos('.', $filename))\n        {\n            return '';  //if there's no extension (and allowed_types is set to '*', return an empty string as extension.\n            //this prevents returning the whole ORIGINAL file name as extension <- severe privacy flaw if filename encryption is enabled.\n        }\n        else\n        {\n            $x = explode('.', $filename);   //if there's at least one '.', take the last one as extension delimiter.\n            return '.'.end($x);\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\nThank you for your attention.\n","closed_by":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1349/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/1349/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}